des:
Bruh Sounds presents the world's first interactive Bruh conversation generator!
Just say "bruh" and Bruh Sounds will start a fun-filled bruh-versation with you.

If you need someone to talk to, chat with Bruh Sounds. He's always ready for some "bruh talk" to entertain you.

As seen-in-the-meme, Bruh Sounds contains 100% accurate bruh sound effects, plus dozens of bruh-fluenced sounds to keep you laughing.

Just say to your Echo device, "Alexa, open Bruh Sounds."
